727828f-a.text:
New Calvary Cemetery (Queens): The entrance to the cemetery on the south side of Queens Boulevard, between 51st and 58th Streets.

P.L. Sperr June 7, 1927

727827f-a.text:
Queens Boulevard, west from and across 51st Street, toward the subway 'El' on Roosevelt Avenue. The frame house on the right stands in the path of the proposed extension of 51st Street.
P. L. Sperr  June 7, 1927
